Description: This package are R Bindings to the FORT myrmidon C++ API,
 a library to analyze the tracking data made by the FORmicidae Tracker
 system. It lest you access all primitive defined in the FORT GUI,
 like the Ant obkject, their metadata, their identification priitive
 (relation to a TagID), measurement. It can also perfom complex
 queries to identify Ant duringt the experiment, detect their
 collision with other individual, construct their trajectories and
 finally estimate their timed intercation with other individuals.
